Per the FCC docs... *This device is manufactured by [[SerComm]]. :"AKW00B-1.6" is silkscreened on the main board. *[[Broadcom]] BCM6361UKFEBG WiSoC :an ''ESMT'' F59L1G81A-25T 1Gb (128MB) :NAND Flash ''Nanya'' NT5TU64M16GG-AC *Wireless module for the 5GHz radio :using BCM4352 (BCM4352KMLG) with :2x [https://estore.rfmd.com/RFMD_OnlineStore/Products/RFMD%20Parts/PID-P_RFFM4501.aspx?DC=25 '''RFMD''' RFFM4501 802.11a/n/ac FEMs] :"AHL00D-1.0" is silkscreened on the back of the module. *The two (''NETGEAR'' branded w/ ''patent pending'') antenna types :in use are 401-10006-01 (2.4GHz) and 401-10007-01 (5GHz).
